title: Did Baker Mayfield violate NFL etiquette? - Brady Quinn Football Show (Football 10/9)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and John Breech to cover news of the day including Sam Darnold's return (3:55), potential concerns over the Chiefs (14:40), which is followed by an extensive breakdown of HandshakeGate from Monday night between Baker Mayfield and the 49ers (24:00). The guys also discuss bad teams with potentially bright futures (34:00), the Redskins culture (41:30) and problems in Dallas (48:00).
